      "name": "Solver Verification Against FDA Benchmark Geometry",
      "description": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2023R2) was verified against the FDA nozzle benchmark dataset (FDA-HHC-2011-D002). Velocity profiles at five axial stations matched experimental PIV data within 5% RMS error. Solver settings were frozen prior to the pump simulation campaign.",
      "prov:wasGeneratedBy": "https://uofa.net/morrison/activity/solver-verification-fda-nozzle-2024"
    }
